## Hit normalization

Hit normalization (title/section/content with `<mark>` highlighting and snippet truncation around the first match) is ported from [`assets/scripts/components/instantsearch/getHitData.js`](https://github.com/DataDog/documentation/blob/master/assets/scripts/components/instantsearch/getHitData.js). The Typesense-native `highlights[]` array is folded into the same normalized shape Hugo produces from instantsearch.js's `_highlightResult`.
